<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{% block title %}Broceliande Immo{% endblock %}</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="{{ url('public/css/style.css') }}?v={{ 'now'|date('YmdHis') }}" rel="stylesheet">
    {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark fixed-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="{{ url() }}">
                <i class="bi bi-house-heart-fill"></i> Broceliande Immo
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="{{ url('annonces/vente') }}">
                            <i class="bi bi-house-door"></i> Acheter
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="{{ url('annonces/location') }}">
                            <i class="bi bi-key"></i> Louer
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="{{ url('contact') }}">
                            <i class="bi bi-envelope"></i> Contact
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <!-- Section de connexion supprimée -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main style="margin-top: 56px;">
        {% block content %}{% endblock %}
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5><i class="bi bi-house-heart"></i> Broceliande Immo</h5>
                    <p>Votre partenaire immobilier de confiance en Bretagne. Découvrez des biens d'exception dans un cadre mythique.</p>
                    <div class="social-links">
                        <a href="#" class="me-3"><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="me-3"><i class="bi bi-instagram"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="me-3"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>Liens utiles</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><a href="{{ url('mentions-legales') }}" class="text-decoration-none"><i class="bi bi-chevron-right"></i> Mentions légales</a></li>
                        <li><a href="{{ url('politique-confidentialite') }}" class="text-decoration-none"><i class="bi bi-chevron-right"></i> Politique de confidentialité</a></li>
                        <li><a href="{{ url('contact') }}" class="text-decoration-none"><i class="bi bi-chevron-right"></i> Contact</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>Contact</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i> 1 rue de Brocéliande, 35380 Paimpont</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-telephone"></i> 02 99 12 34 56</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-envelope"></i> contact@broceliande-immo.fr</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-clock"></i> Lun-Ven: 9h-18h</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="text-center">
                <small>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Broceliande Immo. Tous droits réservés.</small>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    {% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}
</body>
</html>
